KARACHI, Mar 04 (APP): Speaker of the Provincial Assembly (PA) of Sindh Agha Siraj Durrani has adjourned a session of the PA scheduled to be held on Thursday (March 04), now the same would be held on Friday (March 05) at 10a.m.
The order was made by the Speaker in exercise of the powers conferred upon him under Rule 29 of Rules of Procedure of the Provincial Assembly of Sindh.
